**Steps to Reproduce**:

Compile the following code fragment with **IDE0051** enabled:
```c#
internal static class Polyfill_Int32
{
    extension(int i)
    {
        public bool IsZero()
        {
            return IsZeroHelper(i);
        }

        private static bool IsZeroHelper(int value)
        {
            return value == 0;
        }
    }
}
```

**Expected Behavior**:

**IDE0051** is not reported.

